    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AddonCategory
    Enumeration AddonCategory is a subclass of ICategory and represents all Minecraft IntegrationType.ADDON categories
    Author
    Interface Author represents a person registered on a platform who has created a Minecraft integration
    Authority
    Class Authority contains private wrapper classes for each supported integration platform which implements the Author interface
    Authority.CurseforgeWrapper
     
    Authority.ModrinthWrapper
     
    Authority.SpigetWrapper
     
    CustomizationCategory
    Enumeration CustomizationCategory is a subclass of ICategory and represents all IntegrationType.CUSTOMIZATION categories
    DatapackCategory
    Enumeration DatapackCategory is a subclass of ICategory and represents all IntegrationType.DATAPACK categories
    ICategory
    Interface ICategory is a representation of a Minecraft category and is used to group Integrations.
    ILoader
    Interface ILoader is a representation of a Minecraft loader.
    Integration
     
    IntegrationFile
     
    Integrations
    Interface containing static LazyIntegrations of the most popular integrations for faster access
    IntegrationType
    Enumeration IntegrationType represents all possible types of Minecraft integrations
    LazyIntegration
    Record class with Platform and String id required in constructor.
    ModCategory
    Enumeration ModCategory is a subclass of ICategory and represents all IntegrationType.MOD categories
    Modding
    Class Modding contains private wrapper classes for each supported integration platform which implements the Integration interface
    Modding.CurseforgeWrapper
     
    Modding.ModrinthWrapper
     
    Modding.SpigetWrapper
     
    ModLoader
    Enumeration ModLoader is a subclass of ILoader and represents all IntegrationType.MOD loaders
    ModpackCategory
    Enumeration ModpackCategory is a subclass of ICategory and represents all IntegrationType.MODPACK categories
    Organisation
    Interface Organisation is a subclass of Team and represents an organization which has an owner
    Platform
    Enumeration Platform represents all supported and the most popular platforms for posting Minecraft integrations
    Platform.Wrapper
    The main abstract wrapper class for all platforms wrappers.
    PluginCategory
    Enumeration PluginCategory is a subclass of ICategory and represents all IntegrationType.PLUGIN categories
    PluginLoader
    Enumeration PluginLoader is a subclass of ILoader and represents all IntegrationType.PLUGIN loaders ever made
    ResourcepackCategory
    Enumeration ResourcepackCategory is a subclass of ICategory and represents all IntegrationType.RESOURCEPACK categories
    ShaderCategory
    Enumeration ShaderCategory is a subclass of ICategory and represents all IntegrationType.SHADER categories
    ShaderLoader
    Enumeration ShaderLoader is a subclass of ILoader and represents all IntegrationType.SHADER loaders including VANILLA as standart
    Side
    Enumeration for Minecraft environment sides which could be CLIENT, SERVER or ANY
    Status
    Enumeration Status represents all possible integration statuses
    Team
    Team interface is an @{link Iterable} of Author and is a named group of authors
    Version
    Record class Version represents a Minecraft version with ILoader and version required
    WorldCategory
    Enumeration WorldCategory is a subclass of ICategory and represents all IntegrationType.WORLD categories
